OL,3,CLiverpool sack head coach Arne Slot
OL,5,FLiverpool FC have sacked head coach
OL,6,FArne Slot after a disappointing
OL,7,Fdefence of their Premier League title.
OL,9,FIn a statement, the club confimed that
OL,10,FMr Slot would be leaving his role
OL,11,F"with immediate effect", adding "he
OL,12,Fleaves with a Premier League title to
OL,13,Fhis name and our deepest gratitude and
OL,14,Fappreciation."
OL,16,FThe 47 year old replaced Jurgen Klopp
OL,17,Fwho stepped down at Anfield after nine
OL,18,Fyears as manager.
