OL,3,CLiverpool sack head coach Arne Slot
OL,5,FJoining the club in the summer of
OL,6,F2024, Slot steered LFC to their 20th
OL,7,Fleague title in his debut season.
OL,9,FBut the team struggled during his
OL,10,Fsecond year in the post, and the
OL,11,FDutchman accepted he did not always
OL,12,Fmake the right decisions, after their
OL,13,Ftitle defence ended with a fifth-place
OL,14,Ffinish in the Premier League.
OL,16,FMore to follow.
